00:43:00,680 --> 00:43:02,440
Aku tak tahan kebohongan.

721
00:43:06,760 --> 00:43:09,080
Kau tak tahan hanya itu?

722
00:43:09,400 --> 00:43:10,360
Bohong?

723
00:43:11,280 --> 00:43:13,400
Brengsek, kau tak tahan banyak.

724
00:43:13,720 --> 00:43:16,800
Orang bohong untuk memudahkan hidup.

725
00:43:17,440 --> 00:43:19,120
Agar tak terluka, menderita.

726
00:43:19,520 --> 00:43:21,040
Jangan sakiti siapa pun.

727
00:43:22,160 --> 00:43:24,640
- Lupakan, Samu.
- Aku tak yakin... Marina!

728
00:43:25,800 --> 00:43:26,920
Marina!

729
00:43:31,760 --> 00:43:32,720
Marina!

730
00:44:11,000 --> 00:44:13,560
Itu baru anakku.
